{"tid":786331,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"S Pen 唔用鋰電池　Samsung Note 9 運用電動車新充電技術","createTime":"2018-08-20T00:05:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T08:20:15.000Z","uid":81228,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"30d880a9760820865d5340dbc496bbe57acd537a","tid":786331,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T00:05:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1764316/org/a7a7d6b8071c59268356bb98a3d33ce4.jpeg/nyAmEUnFOGJUdkla593g7ne0RRlkhBPXvIuyRbyLskU?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1764316%2Forg%2Fa7a7d6b8071c59268356bb98a3d33ce4.jpeg%2FnyAmEUnFOGJUdkla593g7ne0RRlkhBPXvIuyRbyLskU%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=590be51b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSamsung Galaxy Note 9 的最大賣點，就是在 S Pen 加入藍牙低電耗（BLE）遙控功能。到底細小的 S Pen 如何放得下鋰電池？原來 Samsung 是使用了一項近年應用於電動車的新充電技術，取代鋰電池為 S Pen 充電。<br />\n<br />\nSamsung Galaxy Note 9 的 S Pen 只需充電 40 秒，就可以提供 30 分鐘備用或 200 次按鍵的電量，原來使用的並非大家熟悉的鋰電池，而是用上了在部分電動車中已經有應用的超級電容器（Supercapacitor），為 S Pen 提供電力。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1764651/org/c9a30b6bdb25c6b6dcd6126663384732.jpg/61XmqLB1En-YDVcypcWiNGb4qYumYCg6b30exG99HsQ?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1764651%2Forg%2Fc9a30b6bdb25c6b6dcd6126663384732.jpg%2F61XmqLB1En-YDVcypcWiNGb4qYumYCg6b30exG99HsQ%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=52543493&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSamsung Galaxy Note 9 的 S Pen 使用超級電容器技術，取代大家熟悉的鋰電池。（林勇攝）<br />\n<br />\n著名科技網站 TheVerge 近日就因為 S Pen 的技術，採訪了英國 University College London 的 Thomas Miller 及美國 Drexel University 的 Yury Gogotsi 兩位主力研究超級電容器的學者，解釋 S Pen 的新技術。<br />\n<br />\n超級電容器跟大家日常生活中，例如電光管中的電容器原理相若，是利用兩片不同電極的導電體，將電流儲存在導電體的表面。比起日常使用的電容器，超級電容器可以在比例上儲存更大量的電力。由於電容器儲存電量跟導電體的面積成正比，所以近年的超級電容器開發用上了好像石墨一類的新物料，去擴大可以儲電的面積。Thomas Miller 就提到，若果要以超級電容器去製作手機電池，大小將會接近一罐可樂。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1764660/org/e45a1577bffe1643b8be55cda2be3672.jpg/d6PWSCfnHQcym652GKpDXHB90fQKp2W20kWQ0tJFkNI?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1764660%2Forg%2Fe45a1577bffe1643b8be55cda2be3672.jpg%2Fd6PWSCfnHQcym652GKpDXHB90fQKp2W20kWQ0tJFkNI%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=9cdaaefb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nS Pen 以超級電容器取代鋰電池，有著充電快速而且可以上萬次反覆充電的優點。（Samsung）<br />\n<br />\n超級電容器充電時間遠比鋰電池短，而且能夠多次反覆充電。眾所周知，鋰電池會隨著反覆充電，又壽命不斷減少，而超級電容器則可以反覆充電萬次以上，所以更適合用於 S Pen 的設計；Yury Gogotsi 更指出，S Pen 的電池很大機會比 Note 9 本身有更長的壽命。由於超級電容器是以靜電方式在導電體表面儲存電力，比較起鋰電池需要透過化學反應轉電力轉換，效率得以大幅提升。不過超級電容器雖然充電極快速而且可以反覆使用，但其電量始終受到導電體面積所限，現時只適用於一些細件的周邊配件。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1764663/org/225b16c79c3fc093203fad322b6ca8bb.jpg/W1du69-FEpK33D6AUo2egn_1XVU8cv9GW8SPKVvEjyk?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1764663%2Forg%2F225b16c79c3fc093203fad322b6ca8bb.jpg%2FW1du69-FEpK33D6AUo2egn_1XVU8cv9GW8SPKVvEjyk%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=861a6437&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n超級電容器可以儲存的電量受大小限制，不過 S Pen 除了遙控之外的基本功能，在沒有電力下依然可以使用。（Samsung）<br />\n<br />\n現時上海已經電動巴士使用超級電容器技術，巴士在每個車站快速充電，每次電力足夠應該 10 至 15 分鐘的路程。現時業界主力將超級電容器跟儲電池混合使用，希望以兩者的特性互補不足。例如將超級電容器應用在電動車的停車及起動上面，去減少短時間的電力釋放對鋰電池構成的損害。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：區慶威<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/224483/s-pen-%E5%94%94%E7%94%A8%E9%8B%B0%E9%9B%BB%E6%B1%A0-samsung-note-9-%E9%81%8B%E7%94%A8%E9%9B%BB%E5%8B%95%E8%BB%8A%E6%96%B0%E5%85%85%E9%9B%BB%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2595%25B8%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25B4%25BB%2F224483%2Fs-pen-%25E5%2594%2594%25E7%2594%25A8%25E9%258B%25B0%25E9%259B%25BB%25E6%25B1%25A0-samsung-note-9-%25E9%2581%258B%25E7%2594%25A8%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%258B%2595%25E8%25BB%258A%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2585%2585%25E9%259B%25BB%25E6%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%2593&d=%2BmEGqCqhMWI0lOc0EbPP9S7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=4a43c589\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/224483/s-pen-%E5%94%94%E7%94%A8%E9%8B%B0%E9%9B%BB%E6%B1%A0-samsung-note-9-%E9%81%8B%E7%94%A8%E9%9B%BB%E5%8B%95%E8%BB%8A%E6%96%B0%E5%85%85%E9%9B%BB%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93</a>"},{"pid":"77b3d2cf60d234c1efb0c554267936dcdf1de243","tid":786331,"uid":10904,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T00:15:24.000Z","msg":"用Supercap 都係新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9729c1b1d95b38f2aad0bed97212108a00b45986","tid":786331,"uid":36673,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T00:17:46.000Z","msg":"????<br />\n當年收購一半Wacom technology 唔係就係支筆唔洗電咩"},{"pid":"45e40c78acae6e46cfd90f251615adae1df08187","tid":786331,"uid":182286,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T00:19:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"381c41ff14b4db7d44b3ce260159dca7da4f8184","tid":786331,"uid":49693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9729c1b1d95b38f2aad0bed97212108a00b45986","tid":786331,"uid":36673,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T00:17:46.000Z","msg":"????<br />\n當年收購一半Wacom technology 唔係就係支筆唔洗電咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T14:16:04.000Z","msg":"5%股權咋,邊度有50%呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"321e989c97b2e204b43aa341b41de764630363f0","tid":786331,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T23:04:50.000Z","msg":"咪即係Cap<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c157004a4721dcb41ba0a9e4141156dfaa27232c","tid":786331,"uid":144113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T03:49:53.000Z","msg":"咁撚嘩眾取寵嘅標題，原來係01<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a151ac032d0ddd27678c02e5eb93c1ac0711df7","tid":786331,"uid":82587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T23:47:18.000Z","msg":"***發明c